start using Better Diary, you should know:</p>
<h2>Work on entries</h2>
<ul>
    <li><b>Add new entry</b> by tapping on <b>+</b> icon in the bottom right corner.<br>
        You can also format content, insert media (photos, sound) and pick emoticons, mood, weather and location for the entry</li>
    <li><b>Edit entry</b> by clicking on the entry to open and then tapping on Edit (pen) icon</li>
    <li><b>Delete entry</b> by long-click on the entry and select Delete (trash bin) icon</li>
</ul>
<h2>Work on diaries</h2>
<ul>
    <li><b>Share diary</b>: you need to sign in for sharing. In your diary page (Timeline), tapping "Circle" icon on action bar to invite people from contact book.<br>
        There are two sharing options: Read & write | Read only, so make sure you select desired option for invited people.</li>
    <li><b>New diary</b> is created by clicking on "New" icon from app drawer (after expanding diary list)</li>
    <li><b>Sync data</b>: your all diaries are synced immediately across devices when you click on "Sync" icon from app drawer (after expanding diary list)</li>
    <li><b>Rename and Delete</b> diary is easy from its options</li>
</ul>
<h2>Customize diary looking</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Decorate your diary with many font styles, themes by changing Settings -> Look & Feel</li>
</ul>
<h2>Protect your data</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Set the app secure access by setting passcode in Settings -> Security. And remember to regularly backup your data through Settings -> Backup & restore</li>
</ul>
<h2>Others</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Beside Timeline, you can browse past entries by Calendar, Atlas(maps), Tag</li>
    <li>Change some advanced configurations from Settings -> Advanced</li>

<h2>Work on entries</h2>
<ul>
    <li><b>Add new entry</b> by tapping on <b>+</b> icon in the bottom right corner.<br>
        You can also format content, insert media (photos, sound) and pick emoticons, mood, weather and location for the entry</li>
    <li><b>Edit entry</b> by clicking on the entry to open and then tapping on Edit (pen) icon</li>
    <li><b>Delete entry</b> by long-click on the entry and select Delete (trash bin) icon</li>
</ul>
<h2>Work on diaries</h2>
<ul>
    <li><b>Share diary</b>: you need to sign in for sharing. In your diary page (Timeline), tapping "Circle" icon on action bar to invite people from contact book.<br>
        There are two sharing options: Read & write | Read only, so make sure you select desired option for invited people.</li>
    <li><b>New diary</b> is created by clicking on "New" icon from app drawer (after expanding diary list)</li>
    <li><b>Sync data</b>: your all diaries are synced immediately across devices when you click on "Sync" icon from app drawer (after expanding diary list)</li>
    <li><b>Rename and Delete</b> diary is easy from its options</li>
</ul>
<h2>Customize diary looking</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Decorate your diary with many font styles, themes by changing Settings -> Look & Feel</li>
</ul>
<h2>Protect your data</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Set the app secure access by setting passcode in Settings -> Security. And remember to regularly backup your data through Settings -> Backup & restore</li>
</ul>
<h2>Others</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Beside Timeline, you can browse past entries by Calendar, Atlas(maps), Tag</li>
    <li>Change some advanced configurations from Settings -> Advanced</li>
</ul>
